casebody.data:
AUTOMATIC DRIVING SCHOOL, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPARTMENT OF HIGHWAY SAFETY AND MOTOR VEHICLES, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1401 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 13, 2017

ORDERED that the joint stipulation for voluntary dismissal of appeal is recognized by the Court, and this administrative appeal from the State of Florida, Department of Highway Safety and Motor Vehicles is hereby dismissed.
